When this flag is set to true, the listener hands off redirected connections to the listener associated with the original destination address. If there is no listener associated with the original destination address, the connection is handled by the listener that receives it. Defaults to false.
设置为true,表明监听器将接收到的请求转交给和请求原目的地址关联的listener进行处理。
